OL,3,CFamily's tribute to 'kindest' man, 73,
OL,4,Cwho died following alleged attack
OL,6,FThe family of a 73-year-old man who
OL,7,Fdied following an alleged assault in
OL,8,FCheltenham last week have described
OL,9,Fhim as a "one of the kindest people
OL,10,Fyou could meet".
OL,12,FPolice say Jim Davies died in hospital
OL,13,Ftwo days after he was reportedly
OL,14,Fpunched in the face following an
OL,15,Fexchange with two teenage boys on
OL,16,FHoneybourne Way on 8 April.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
