OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1776355855
OL,3,CFamily's tribute to 'kindest' man, 73,
OL,4,Cwho died following alleged attack
OL,6,FTwo teenage boys were arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of the pensioner's murder.
OL,8,FOne, aged 16, has been released with
OL,9,Fno further action and another, aged
OL,10,F17, remains on bail while police
OL,11,Fenquiries continue.
OL,13,FMr Davies' family have paid tribute to
OL,14,Fhim, describing him as a "kind and
OL,15,Fcompassionate man, a friend to many
OL,16,Fand a consummate storyteller."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
