FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1776355855
OL,3,CFamily's tribute to 'kindest' man, 73,
OL,4,Cwho died following alleged attack
OL,6,FIn a statement, they said: "We as a
OL,7,Ffamily are devastated by the loss of
OL,8,FJimmy. He was a friend to so many, but
OL,9,Fto me and my family he was a much-
OL,10,Floved uncle, brother and brother-in-
OL,11,Flaw.
OL,13,F"Jimmy was one of the kindest people
OL,14,Fanyone could have the pleasure of
OL,15,Fmeeting, he was caring, compassionate,
OL,16,Fand always putting others first.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1776355855
OL,3,CFamily's tribute to 'kindest' man, 73,
OL,4,Cwho died following alleged attack
OL,6,F"He made sure no one around him ever
OL,7,Ffelt alone, and his love of
OL,8,Fmotorcycles brought him into contact
OL,9,Fwith many people, forming friendships
OL,10,Fwherever he went.
OL,12,F"With a natural warmth and a gift for
OL,13,Fstorytelling, he shared his life with
OL,14,Fgreat joy and, in doing so, touched a
OL,15,Fremarkable number of lives.
OL,17,F"Our lives will never be the same
OL,18,Fwithout him, and we know that many
OL,19,Fothers will share in the sadness we
OL,20,Ffeel."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
